::Battera::

She heard the bot yelling down on the ground at her.  She swooped down and 
landed next to him.
"What?"
She couldn't understand why this bot was acting so strangely towards her.  
"Why are you so worried about my wing.  It's damaged and so what.  Why would 
you care.  Why worry about a coward like me."
She flew up into the tree that was next to Cybershark and tried to hide in 
the branches.  She was ashamed of herself and didn't want to have others 
waste thier time on a coward.

::CyberShark::

    "Wait!! I only wish to talk!" CyberShark called out to Battera. He
started to fly after her. "I don't even know you name and you look hurt. 
What
the?" He said, noticing the flying pterosaur (actual name of group). It was
red in color, he scanned it and found it to be a Predacon.
    "That's funny I don't recall any Predacons being pterosaurs." CyberShark
said to himself. "No matter my primary concern is that bat. Hey! Stop for a
sec, you look injured, my base isn't far from here, you could get repaired."
